      <title>小罗伯特·肯尼迪 (RFK Jr.) 任命妮可·沙纳汉 (Nicole Shanahan) 为白宫竞选搭档</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/kennedy-taps-shanahan-as-running-mate-in-white-house-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小罗伯特·F·肯尼迪 (Robert F. Kennedy Jr.) 正在任命慈善家和科技企业家妮可·沙纳汉 (Nicole Shanahan) 作为他的竞选搭档，此举旨在提高他在女性和民主党选民中的独立总统竞选水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/kennedy-taps-shanahan-as-running-mate-in-white-house-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 19:33:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
